A cozy home study corner at night in Studio Ghibli style, featuring a warm desk lamp illuminating an open laptop displaying colorful code, surrounded by scattered university-style notebooks and a steaming cup of tea. Through a large window, a whimsical starlit sky with floating geometric shapes representing algorithms and data structures drifts past like gentle spirits. A curious cat sits on a stack of thick programming textbooks, watching the screen with interest. Soft watercolor textures, warm amber and deep blue color palette, with gentle dust motes catching the lamplight, conveying the magic of self-directed learning and the joy of returning to foundational knowledge from the comfort of home.
